         <component>
            <section ID="s25">
               <id root="cb248bd2-f000-7f7a-9388-8aad78848444"/>
               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph ID="p13181281409676478">Cystografin (Diatrizoate Meglumine
Injection USP 30%) is available in 200 mL and 400 mL bottles containing
100 mL and 300 mL of Cystografin respectively with sufficient capacity
for dilution up to 167 mL and 350 mL respectively.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20150316"/>
               <component>
                  <section ID="s25.1">
                     <id root="4230deb6-9080-ca96-8c18-c22b49d499e7"/>
                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <title>Storage</title>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph ID="p13261281409676478">Store at 20-25°C (68-77°F) [See
USP]. Protect from light.</paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20150316"/>
                  </section>
               </component>
               <component>
                  <section ID="s25.2">
                     <id root="bf06c61b-595a-ebfa-ae8c-242280119e4c"/>
                     <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
                     <title>Also Available</title>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph ID="p15421281409676478">Cystografin Dilute (Diatrizoate
Meglumine Injection USP 18%) is also available, as a 300 mL fill in
a 400 mL bottle.</paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20150316"/>
                  </section>
               </component>
            </section>
         </component>
